ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing real-world sales data from Zepto, a quick-commerce platform. The objective of this project is to perform data cleaning, exploratory data analysis (EDA), aggregation, and visualization using Python.

The dataset contains over 200,000 sales transaction records along with a product catalog. Through this project, I implemented a complete data analysis workflow â€” from raw data processing to generating meaningful business insights.

